Powders will be measured with a #knife

Mix @sodium bicarbonate{1%knife tip} with @citric acid{1%knife tip}

Whip @egg white{1} into the prepared mixture

Immediately shape into thin meringues with a #spoon

Dry ~{4%hours} in a #dehydrator
